title: Newly Renovated 3 Bed/3 Bath + Den/Office - Panoramic Views !!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-Three, Lighted Tennis Courts Featuring a Versacourt System', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-Extra stuff?', 'Convenient Storage Lockers Available', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
